  "changelog": "# Sharkord Desktop v0.5.50 Beta\n\n## Added\n\n- Capability-gated GIF attachment controls for Kanuracer servers.\n- Capability-gated message reaction controls for Kanuracer servers.\n- Capability-gated security event clearing and security audit log UI.\n\n## Changed\n\n- Original/upstream servers keep these Kanuracer-only controls hidden unless the server advertises support.\n- German/English UI copy updated for the new media and security admin states.\n\n## Verification\n\n- Frontend tests: passed.\n- Frontend development and production builds: OK.\n- Go tests: OK.\n- Human QA: server connect, settings, audio, server security, chat controls smoke OK.\n- Linux and Windows release artifacts built.\n- macOS artifact skipped for this beta.\n\nStable channel stays unchanged.\n",
